  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grow, feed and care for your colony of adorable isopods in this realistic semi-idle simulator. Watch your isopods multiply and split or sell your colony if they become too numerous. Created by the Kunstaat community, 100% of our proceeds support charity!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All our proceeds support New Incentives. One of the most effective charities in the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Isopod Keeping Simulator is a project made by the community join the discord to contribute to the development. You can even contribute without any prior experience by doing research.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Work In Progress:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384120/extras/8721c6fd3821bbc8185ba332c8355a50.poster.avif?t=1769896638\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384120/extras/8721c6fd3821bbc8185ba332c8355a50.webm?t=1769896638\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384120/extras/8721c6fd3821bbc8185ba332c8355a50.mp4?t=1769896638\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Realistic isopod behavior</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customizable enclosures</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Humidity systems</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Idle game style progress mechanics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique patterns on each isopod</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cute lads</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grow, feed and care for your colony of adorable isopods in this realistic semi-idle simulator. Watch your isopods multiply and split or sell your colony if they become too numerous. Created by the Kunstaat community, 100% of our proceeds support charity!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All our proceeds support New Incentives. One of the most effective charities in the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Isopod Keeping Simulator is a project made by the community join the discord to contribute to the development. You can even contribute without any prior experience by doing research.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Work In Progress:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384120/extras/8721c6fd3821bbc8185ba332c8355a50.poster.avif?t=1769896638\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384120/extras/8721c6fd3821bbc8185ba332c8355a50.webm?t=1769896638\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384120/extras/8721c6fd3821bbc8185ba332c8355a50.mp4?t=1769896638\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Realistic isopod behavior</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customizable enclosures</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Humidity systems</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Idle game style progress mechanics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique patterns on each isopod</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cute lads</p></li></ul>",
